ANYTHING ON IT.

395
00:17:48,134 --> 00:17:49,570
[AKATSUKI]
WHICH MEANS...

396
00:17:49,670 --> 00:17:53,173
[NAOTSUGU] IT MUST BE ONE OF
THE NEW NOVASPHERE MONSTERS.

397
00:17:53,273 --> 00:17:56,910
[SHIROE] IT'S HUGE,
BUT IT'S LEVEL 68.

398
00:17:57,010 --> 00:17:59,513
IT LOOKS LIKE A GIANT
MASS OF DEBUFFS.

399
00:17:59,613 --> 00:18:02,649
[AKATSUKI] IS IT THE REASON
THE DUNGEON'S FALLING APART?

400
00:18:02,749 --> 00:18:04,017
[SHIROE] PROBABLY.

401
00:18:04,117 --> 00:18:06,853
IT'S A LITTLE RISKY,
BUT WE DON'T HAVE A CHOICE.

402
00:18:06,953 --> 00:18:08,054
TAKE IT OUT.

403
00:18:08,154 --> 00:18:09,255
[NAOTSUGU]
ALL RIGHT!

404
00:18:09,355 --> 00:18:11,324
LET'S MAKE THIS QUICK,
STRATEGY MAN!

405
00:18:11,424 --> 00:18:12,659
[AKATSUKI] HUH!
[SHIROE] UH!

406
00:18:12,759 --> 00:18:14,695
[NAOTSUGU] I GOT SOMETHING
FOR YOU, RAT FACE!

407
00:18:14,795 --> 00:18:16,229
(SHIMMER)

408
00:18:17,463 --> 00:18:18,699
UH! UH!

409
00:18:18,799 --> 00:18:21,401
[AKATSUKI]
STEALTH BLADE!

410
00:18:22,202 --> 00:18:24,337
[NAOTSUGU]
CROSS SLASH!

411
00:18:24,437 --> 00:18:25,906
[SHIROE] NO MATTER
HOW GOOD YOU ARE,

412
00:18:26,006 --> 00:18:27,674
FIGHTING LIKE THIS
IS TOTALLY DIFFERENT!

413
00:18:27,774 --> 00:18:30,811
[NAOTSUGU] NO KIDDING! YOU CAN'T
REPRODUCE THE SIZE OF THIS THING

414
00:18:30,911 --> 00:18:34,848
OR ITS BAD BREATH WITH A
MONITOR AND A SET OF SPEAKERS!

415
00:18:34,948 --> 00:18:36,650
COME ON!

416
00:18:39,052 --> 00:18:41,054
[SHIROE]
THORN BIND HOSTAGE!

417
00:18:41,154 --> 00:18:43,056
[NAOTSUGU] NICE!

418
00:18:43,156 --> 00:18:45,158
[AKATSUKI] UH!

419
00:18:47,460 --> 00:18:49,963
[NAOTSUGU] LOOKS LIKE IT HAS
A HIGH SHIELD RATING.

420
00:18:50,063 --> 00:18:51,898
BUT WE STILL
HAVE 3 VINES LEFT.

421
00:18:51,998 --> 00:18:53,299
SIC 'EM, STUMPY!

422
00:18:53,399 --> 00:18:55,602
DON'T CALL ME THAT!

423
00:18:55,702 --> 00:18:57,571
[NAOTSUGU] UH!

424
00:18:57,671 --> 00:19:00,473
[SHIROE] LET'S MAKE SURE
YOU DON'T MISS.

425
00:19:00,574 --> 00:19:02,142
MIND SHOCK!

426
00:19:04,144 --> 00:19:05,311
[SHIROE, VOICE‐OVER]
ADD A CONFUSION DEBUFF

427
00:19:05,411 --> 00:19:07,548
THAT LOWERS ACCURACY
AND AGILITY.

428
00:19:07,648 --> 00:19:10,884
NEXT, AMPLIFY THE ATTACK POWER
OF YOUR ALLIES' WEAPONS.

429
00:19:10,984 --> 00:19:12,285
(NAOTSUGU SCREAMS)

