00:19:16,723 --> 00:19:18,925
[SHIROE] KEEN EDGE.

431
00:19:19,025 --> 00:19:20,026
[AKATSUKI]
THANKS FOR THAT.

432
00:19:20,126 --> 00:19:21,294
GOING IN!

433
00:19:21,394 --> 00:19:24,865
ONE MORE HIT AND
WE'RE DONE WITH THIS!

434
00:19:27,734 --> 00:19:29,770
ASSASSINATION!

435
00:19:30,871 --> 00:19:33,473
[NAOTSUGU] HUH! HUH.

436
00:19:57,263 --> 00:19:58,832
[SHIROE] AWESOME.

437
00:19:58,932 --> 00:20:00,100
[AKATSUKI]
THE WIND IS COLD.

438
00:20:00,200 --> 00:20:01,968
[NAOTSUGU] AH HA HA!
BUT IT FEELS GREAT.

439
00:20:02,068 --> 00:20:07,307
I THINK IT'S SAFE
TO SAY THE HARD
PART'S BEHIND US.

440
00:20:08,041 --> 00:20:09,175
[AKATSUKI] IT'S BEAUTIFUL.

441
00:20:09,275 --> 00:20:11,578
[NAOTSUGU] IT'S AMAZING.

442
00:20:13,279 --> 00:20:15,015
[KANAMI] THE BEST PART
ABOUT ADVENTURES

443
00:20:15,115 --> 00:20:17,684
IS ALL THE NEW EXPERIENCES.

444
00:20:18,084 --> 00:20:19,953
HMM.

445
00:20:20,053 --> 00:20:21,888
[SHIROE]
EXPERIENCES, HUH?

446
00:20:21,988 --> 00:20:23,123
[NAOTSUGU] HUH?

447
00:20:23,223 --> 00:20:25,125
[SHIROE] WHEN THIS
WAS JUST A GAME,

448
00:20:25,225 --> 00:20:28,028
A LOT OF PLAYERS CAME
TO THIS SPOT AT DAWN

449
00:20:28,128 --> 00:20:30,731
AND SAW IT ON A MONITOR.

450
00:20:31,898 --> 00:20:37,504
BUT NOW WE'RE THE FIRST
ONES TO MAKE IT HERE.

451
00:20:37,604 --> 00:20:40,974
SERIOUSLY, WE'RE
THE FIRST ADVENTURERS

452
00:20:41,074 --> 00:20:43,544
TO ACTUALLY LIVE THIS.

453
00:20:44,277 --> 00:20:45,979
[NAOTSUGU] HMM.

454
00:20:46,713 --> 00:20:48,081
[SHIROE] HMM.

455
00:20:48,181 --> 00:20:49,616
[NAOTSUGU]
YEAH. GUESS WE ARE.

456
00:20:49,716 --> 00:20:52,452
YOU KNOW, ELDER TALES
HAD GREAT ARTWORK AND ALL,

457
00:20:52,553 --> 00:20:54,921
BUT THIS IS SOMETHING ELSE.

458
00:20:55,021 --> 00:20:56,489
[AKATSUKI] I KNOW.

459
00:20:56,590 --> 00:20:59,893
IT'S LIKE THE FIRST THING WE'VE
EARNED BY WINNING A BATTLE.

460
00:21:01,261 --> 00:21:03,063
(FIRE ROARS)

461
00:21:03,163 --> 00:21:06,466
(SHIVERING)

462
00:21:06,567 --> 00:21:07,734
[THUG 1] DID YOU REALLY THINK

463
00:21:07,834 --> 00:21:09,503
YOU WERE GETTING OUT
OF SUSUKINO THAT EASY?

464
00:21:09,603 --> 00:21:11,938
[THUG 2] YOU'VE GOT TO BE
THE WORLD'S BIGGEST MORON

465
00:21:12,038 --> 00:21:13,674
OR JUST INCREDIBLY STUPID.

466
00:21:13,774 --> 00:21:14,575
[TRAVELLER] NO!

467
00:21:14,675 --> 00:21:15,842
(SLAM)
[THUG 3] FOR A BIG WAGON,

468
00:21:15,942 --> 00:21:17,343
I WAS HOPING FOR A
BETTER HAUL THAN THIS.

469
00:21:17,443 --> 00:21:19,279
WHAT ARE YOU
STANDING THERE FOR?

470
00:21:19,379 --> 00:21:21,181
GET BUSY, WILL YOU?

471
00:21:21,281 --> 00:21:23,950
[TOMTOM] I DON'T THINK
I CAN DO THIS.

472
00:21:24,050 --> 00:21:25,185
[THUG 5] FINE.

473
00:21:25,285 --> 00:21:28,121
THEN YOU'RE HEADED
FOR THE CATHEDRAL.

474
00:21:28,221 --> 00:21:29,990
[TOMTOM] DEMICAS?

475
00:21:30,791 --> 00:21:32,058
UH!

476
00:21:33,293 --> 00:21:35,228
[DEMICAS] HOW MANY TIMES
DO I HAVE TO TELL YOU,

477
00:21:35,328 --> 00:21:37,463
DO WHAT I SAY, OR
YOU GET DEALT WITH.

478
00:21:37,564 --> 00:21:39,232
[LONDARK] DON'T WORRY.
YOU'LL COME BACK TO LIFE.

479
00:21:39,332 --> 00:21:41,201
IF PEOPLE STILL GET
UPSET OVER PKING,

480
00:21:41,301 --> 00:21:43,203
THERE'S SOMETHING
WRONG WITH THEM.

481
00:21:43,303 --> 00:21:44,437
[DEMICAS] HEY, GET ALL HIS GEAR

482
00:21:44,538 --> 00:21:47,107
BEFORE HE DISAPPEARS
ON US, GUYS!

483
00:21:47,207 --> 00:21:48,775
[MEN] RIGHT!

484
00:21:48,875 --> 00:21:50,043
(METAL RATTLING)

485
00:21:50,143 --> 00:21:52,078
BETTER NOT
DROP THAT.

486
00:21:52,178 --> 00:21:53,313
[THUG 1] YOU HEARD HIM, NPC.

487
00:21:53,413 --> 00:21:54,748
[THUG 2] YEAH. TAKE
CARE OF OUR STUFF.

488
00:21:54,848 --> 00:21:55,949
HUH?

489
00:21:56,049 --> 00:21:57,651
[THUG 3] FOUND SOME MORE
PEOPLE OF THE LAND, BOSS.

490
00:21:57,751 --> 00:21:59,052
(NPCS CRYING)
YOU THINK THEY MIGHT
KNOW ANYTHING

491
00:21:59,152 --> 00:22:00,754
ABOUT THE GUYS
WE'RE LOOKING FOR?

492
00:22:00,854 --> 00:22:04,390
HUH. NON‐PLAYER CHARACTERS
ARE CRYING NOW.

493
00:22:04,490 --> 00:22:06,492
THAT WASN'T PART OF
THE GAME BEFORE.

494
00:22:06,593 --> 00:22:08,428
[LONDARK]
I COULDN'T CARE LESS.

495
00:22:08,529 --> 00:22:10,797
[THUG] SHOULD WE TAKE
THEM OUT, GUILD MASTER?

496
00:22:10,897 --> 00:22:12,432
(GIRLS SCREAMING)
[DEMICAS] IF YOU WANT.

497
00:22:12,533 --> 00:22:15,001
I DON'T CARE IF THEY'RE
PEOPLE OF THE LAND OR NOT.

498
00:22:15,101 --> 00:22:16,770
THEY DON'T INTEREST ME.

499
00:22:17,337 --> 00:22:19,472
ALL RIGHT, LONDARK.

500
00:22:19,573 --> 00:22:22,375
WHAT ABOUT THE CAT
AND THE HEALER GIRL?

501
00:22:22,475 --> 00:22:24,344
I HAVE MEN
LOOKING FOR THEM.

502
00:22:24,444 --> 00:22:25,646
NOTHING YET.

503
00:22:25,746 --> 00:22:26,780
UGH...

504
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:29,049
[DEMICAS] HOW LONG ARE YOU
GONNA JACK AROUND?!

505
00:22:29,149 --> 00:22:30,250
YOU NEED TO BE OUT THERE

506
00:22:30,350 --> 00:22:32,018
FINDING THAT GIRL
AND THAT CAT FREAK!

507
00:22:32,118 --> 00:22:33,186
[MEN] YES, SIR!

508
00:22:33,286 --> 00:22:34,287
(MEN PANTING)

509
00:22:34,387 --> 00:22:36,389
[DEMICAS]
THIS IS MY WORLD NOW.

510
00:22:36,489 --> 00:22:39,159
AND ANYONE WHO
DEFIES ME WILL PAY.

511
00:22:39,259 --> 00:22:40,360
HA HA HA!

512
00:22:40,460 --> 00:22:42,162
I'M COMING TO GET YOU

513
00:22:42,262 --> 00:22:44,464
AND YOUR DAMN CAT!

514
00:24:14,688 --> 00:24:18,759
[AKATSUKI, VOICE‐OVER]
BRIGANDIA IS A GUILD THAT
RUNS SUSUKINO WITH FORCE.

515
00:24:18,859 --> 00:24:22,362
ITS GUILD MASTER DEMICAS
REIGNS WITH FEAR.

516
00:24:22,462 --> 00:24:26,667
SHIROE'S PARTY MEETS
WITH SERARA AND TRIES
TO ESCAPE THEM.

517
00:24:26,767 --> 00:24:28,735
WHAT STRATEGY DOES
SHIROE IMPLEMENT,

518
00:24:28,835 --> 00:24:32,205
AND WHAT DOES AKATSUKI
SEE DURING THE BATTLE?

519
00:24:33,206 --> 00:24:35,976
[SHIROE]
THIS IS OUR REALITY.

